quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  43,61,"He (Jesus) is, in fact, a sign for the coming of the Hour of Doom. Therefore, have no doubt about its coming, follow me; this is the Right Way"
  43,62,"Let not Satan mislead you, for he is your open enemy"
  43,63,"When Jesus came with clear signs, he stated: \"I have brought you wisdom, and to clarify some of those things about which you have disputes: so fear Allah and obey me"
  43,64,"Surely it is Allah Who is my Lord and your Lord, so worship Him. This is the Right Way"
  43,65,"In spite of these teachings, the factions disagreed among themselves; so woe to the wrongdoers from the punishment of a painful Day"
  43,66,"Are they waiting for the Hour of Doom that it should come on them all of a sudden, without warning"
  43,67,"On that Day, even friends will become enemies to one another with the exception of the righteous people"
  43,68,O My devotees! Today you have nothing to fear or to regret
  43,69,it will be said to those who believed in Our revelations and became Muslims
  43,70,"Enter paradise, you and your spouses; you will be made happy"
  43,71,"There they shall be served with golden dishes and golden goblets, and they shall have everything that their souls can desire and all that their eyes can delight in - and it will be said to them: \"Now you shall abide therein forever"
  43,72,You have inherited this paradise by virtue of your good deeds
  43,73,therein you shall have plenty of fruit to eat